      "span_text": "Indeed, the strong yellow fluorescence of 6C-miR-21-22bp was decreased around 2-fold (3 x10 ) by shortening of anchor sequence into 11 nucleotides (6C-miR-21-11bp), and likewise in the other shortened 6C-miR-21 probes ( Figure 1B )."
